w.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-boasts-about-israel-standing-alone-then-loses-america/0000018f-5eba-d995-a5df-5ebf9ffd0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登对以色列的“末日武器”威胁绝非虚惊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/bidens-doomsday-weapon-threat-to-israel-is-no-false-alarm/0000018f-5e5a-d9a0-a38f-fe7f46f20000</link><description>美国总统威胁停止向以色列运送进攻性武器，可能会损害以色列在北方所依赖的军事能力 ■ 人质协议谈判的分歧并不大，但很大程度上取决于政治考虑 ■ 内塔尼亚胡正中辛瓦尔的下怀，而且哈马斯重新控制加沙地带</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 03:00:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/bidens-doomsday-weapon-threat-to-israel-is-no-false-alarm/0000018f-5e5a-d9a0-a38f-fe7f46f20000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡表示，10 月 7 日的失败“首先”是以色列政府造成的：“人民没有受到保护”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-live/netanyahu-we-hope-to-overcome-disagreements-with-biden-but-we-will-protect-our-country/0000018f-6043-d8a0-a3df-7a635af70000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡：我们希望克服与拜登的分歧，但我们会保护我们的国家 ■ 以色列与哈马斯在开罗的停火谈判没有达成协议，中央情报局局长离开埃及首都 ■ 三名以色列士兵在拉法附近的爆炸中受伤 ■ 白宫：美国不放弃以色列“冲击拉法”无助于击败哈马斯</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 02:17:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article-live/netanyahu-we-hope-to-overcome-disagreements-with-biden-but-we-will-protect-our-country/0000018f-6043-d8a0-a3df-7a635af70000</guid></item><item><title>“我第一次不想在维也纳街头说希伯来语”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-10/ty-article/.highlight/for-the-first-time-i-dont-want-to-speak-hebrew-on-the-streets-of-vienna/0000018f-5f3e-d9a0-a38f-ff3f4cb00000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一位奥地利圣经考古学家前往以色列出差和度假，两名俄罗斯朝圣者前往耶路撒冷以神圣的方式庆祝生日</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 21:59:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2024-05-10/ty-article/.highlight/for-the-first-time-i-dont-want-to-speak-hebrew-on-the-streets-of-vienna/0000018f-5f3e-d9a0-a38f-ff3f4cb00000</guid></item><item><title>国家审计长：以色列军方要求推迟10月7日调查的要求不合理</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/state-comptroller-israeli-militarys-demand-to-delay-october-7-probe-is-unreasonable/0000018f-5f20-d90e-a99f-7f7d82510000</link><description>马塔尼亚胡·恩格尔曼警告说，接受国防机构的立场可能会导致“在很长一段时间内无法对以色列国防军进行任何监督”，并妨碍获取关键证据</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 21:07:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-10/ty-article/.premium/state-comptroller-israeli-militarys-demand-to-delay-october-7-probe-is-unreasonable/0000018f-5f20-d90e-a99f-7f7d82510000</guid></item><item><title>这些犹太裔波兰儿童梦想搬到以色列。大多数人死于大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/these-jewish-polish-boys-dreamed-of-moving-to-israel-most-died-in-the-holocaust/0000018f-5ed3-d9a0-a38f-fef718e90000</link><description>20 世纪 30 年代，犹太裔波兰学童用希伯来语写给他们心爱的老师（当时老师已前往巴勒斯坦）的信件在几十年后被发现，并收录在一本新书中。年轻人一心想在以色列土地上加入老师的行列，但大多数人在大屠杀中被杀害</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 20:53:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/these-jewish-polish-boys-dreamed-of-moving-to-israel-most-died-in-the-holocaust/0000018f-5ed3-d9a0-a38f-fef718e90000</guid></item><item><title>一名前往加沙拯救生命的美国神经外科医生的令人毛骨悚然的证词</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-chilling-testimony-of-a-u-s-neurosurgeon-who-went-to-gaza-to-save-lives/0000018f-5e8a-d995-a5df-5ebf2b890000</link><description>当所有能够逃离加沙的人都在这样做时，大卫·哈桑博士却进行了相反的旅程。他的故事是每个以色列人必读的</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 19:26:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/the-chilling-testimony-of-a-u-s-neurosurgeon-who-went-to-gaza-to-save-lives/0000018f-5e8a-d995-a5df-5ebf2b890000</guid></item><item><title>以色列极右翼抗议者封锁开往加沙的援助卡车</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-protesters-block-gaza-aid-trucks-from-jordan-bound-for-six-hours/0000018f-5e9a-d995-a5df-5ebf73570000</link><description>Tzav 9 组织的抗议者誓言要阻止援助直至所有人质获释，他们在米茨佩·拉蒙 (Mitzpe Ramon) 入口处封锁了 40 辆运往加沙的援助卡车。警方表示，他们没有收到以色列国防军关于卡车抵达的足够警告</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 18:59:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/far-right-israeli-protesters-block-gaza-aid-trucks-from-jordan-bound-for-six-hours/0000018f-5e9a-d995-a5df-5ebf73570000</guid></item><item><title>“这绝对是一场地震”：拜登、比比和武器禁运爆炸事件的美国顶级专家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-09/ty-article/.highlight/definitely-an-earthquake-top-u-s-expert-on-biden-bibi-and-the-arms-embargo-bombshell/0000018f-5e38-d995-a5df-5e3f6cd50000</link><description>美国著名外交政策专家理查德·哈斯剖析了乔·拜登总统决定向以色列政府扣留威力炸弹背后的关键因素</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 18:58:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-05-09/ty-article/.highlight/definitely-an-earthquake-top-u-s-expert-on-biden-bibi-and-the-arms-embargo-bombshell/0000018f-5e38-d995-a5df-5e3f6cd50000</guid></item><item><title>在莫斯科和北京的一点帮助下，以色列输掉了社交媒体之战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-a-little-help-from-moscow-and-beijing-israel-lost-the-social-media-battle/0000018f-5e1a-d82e-a5df-7f1a4a410000</link><description>10 月 7 日之后，数十个志愿者和技术支持的倡议组织起来，以填补以色列政府留下的真空。经过六个月的数字战争，感觉就像一场失败的战斗</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 18:32:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/with-a-little-help-from-moscow-and-beijing-israel-lost-the-social-media-battle/0000018f-5e1a-d82e-a5df-7f1a4a410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警察局长称本-格维尔让他感到恶心：“每天都是争吵和叫喊”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-police-chief-says-ben-gvir-made-him-sick-every-day-its-arguments-and-shouting/0000018f-5e57-d82e-a5df-7f5791a50000</link><description>消息人士称，极右翼国家安全部长向警察局长科比·沙卜泰施加了持续不断的压力，以确保他选出下一任高级警察。然后他在宣布升职的仪式上迟到了</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 18:27:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israels-police-chief-says-ben-gvir-made-him-sick-every-day-its-arguments-and-shouting/0000018f-5e57-d82e-a5df-7f5791a50000</guid></item><item><title>他们的纪录片揭示了以色列的发展方向。这就是他们现在看到的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/their-documentaries-revealed-where-israel-was-heading-this-is-what-they-see-now/0000018f-5d80-d0ec-a9cf-df9f751e0000</link><description>他们之前的纪录片警告了以色列遭受的灾难，但这些导演担心他们的电影是否会有足够的观众来制作</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 17:02:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-05-09/ty-article-magazine/.premium/their-documentaries-revealed-where-israel-was-heading-this-is-what-they-see-now/0000018f-5d80-d0ec-a9cf-df9f751e0000</guid></item><item><title>土耳其在宣布贸易抵制一周后将发放有限的向以色列出口的许可证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/turkey-to-grant-limited-permits-to-export-to-israel-a-week-after-announcing-trade-boycott/0000018f-5dd1-d995-a5df-5ff7f3e00000</link><description>土耳其商人冒着因抵制而遭受经济损失的风险，向埃尔多安施压，要求他重新考虑。但以色列制造商协会负责人认为放松限制只是“一种幻想”</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 16:02:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/turkey-to-grant-limited-permits-to-export-to-israel-a-week-after-announcing-trade-boycott/0000018f-5dd1-d995-a5df-5ff7f3e00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 216 天：据报道以色列谈判小组离开开罗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-216-israeli-negotiation-team-reportedly-leaves-cairo/0000018f-5e03-d9a0-a38f-fe2794fb0001</link><description>中央情报局局长在与内塔尼亚胡和摩萨德负责人会面后返回美国，并在开罗停留 ■ 哈马斯谈判代表团前往多哈，指责以色列试图进入拉法破坏停战谈判 ■ 世卫组织称只剩下三天的燃料加沙南部的医疗行动 ■ 超过 150 名以色列人拦截了前往加沙的约旦援助车队 ■ 战争开始 216 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:50:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-216-israeli-negotiation-team-reportedly-leaves-cairo/0000018f-5e03-d9a0-a38f-fe2794fb0001</guid></item><item><title>人工智能可以成为新闻业的生命线——或者是一根吊死自己的绳子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/ai-could-be-a-lifeline-for-journalism-or-a-rope-to-hang-itself/0000018f-588f-d0ec-a9cf-de9ff6d70000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:24:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/tech-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/ai-could-be-a-lifeline-for-journalism-or-a-rope-to-hang-itself/0000018f-588f-d0ec-a9cf-de9ff6d70000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔在推特上发推文称哈马斯“喜欢”拜登，总统考虑因拉法问题停止美国向以色列运送武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-tweets-hamas-biden-as-president-mulls-halting-u-s-arms-shipments-to-israel/0000018f-5d25-d9a0-a38f-fd27f61e0000</link><description>以色列反对派领导人亚伊尔·拉皮德表示，本·格维尔的推文危及了“每一位以色列国防军士兵和每一位以色列公民”，而财政部长贝扎雷尔·斯莫特里奇则表示，“尽管有拜登的反对，我们仍将在这场战争中取得彻底胜利”</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 13:32:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-tweets-hamas-biden-as-president-mulls-halting-u-s-arms-shipments-to-israel/0000018f-5d25-d9a0-a38f-fd27f61e0000</guid></item><item><title>当以色列人发现我来自爱尔兰时，他们会问：“你为什么恨我们？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-israelis-find-out-im-from-ireland-they-ask-why-do-you-hate-us/0000018f-5cf6-d0ec-a9cf-deff36c10000</link><description>作为一名出生于爱尔兰、居住在特拉维夫的以色列记者，我被迫应对爱尔兰和以色列之间因加沙战争而不断恶化且经常公开敌对的关系。但我在都柏林的朋友和家人提出的一个问题我很难回答</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 13:23:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-05-09/ty-article-opinion/.premium/when-israelis-find-out-im-from-ireland-they-ask-why-do-you-hate-us/0000018f-5cf6-d0ec-a9cf-deff36c10000</guid></item><item><title>国家保险研究所数据显示，自 1851 年以来，已有 5000 多名以色列平民在恐怖袭击中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/over-5-000-israeli-civilians-murdered-in-terror-attacks-since-1851-national-data-shows/0000018f-5d47-d0ec-a9cf-df5f2ce60000</link><description>10月7日，以色列与哈马斯战争爆发，共有822名以色列平民被杀害，造成630名儿童成为孤儿，177人成为寡妇，693名父母失去亲人。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 13:19:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-05-09/ty-article/.premium/over-5-000-israeli-civilians-murdered-in-terror-attacks-since-1851-national-data-shows/0000018f-5d47-d0ec-a9cf-df5f2ce60000</guid></item></channel></rss>